    <item>
      <title>外国投资者对中国刺激计划欢呼雀跃——尽管只是远距离</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreign-investors-cheer-chinas-stimulus-distance-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着市场对中国自疫情爆发以来最大规模刺激计划的兴奋逐渐消退，外国投资者现在开始思考，这笔 1140 亿美元的刺激计划是否能够提供扭转低迷股市所需的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreign-investors-cheer-chinas-stimulus-distance-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 06:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，泰晤士水务公司加紧与债权人谈判，因为解决债务的时间已经所剩无几</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/thames-water-presses-with-creditor-talks-time-resolve-debt-evaporates-sources-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，泰晤士水务公司正在与部分债权人进行谈判，商讨一项 10 亿英镑（13.4 亿美元）的救助计划，以便公司有空间重组 160 亿英镑的债务，并避免破产清算的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/thames-water-presses-with-creditor-talks-time-resolve-debt-evaporates-sources-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 06:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场担心欧洲央行的谨慎政策可能导致通胀低于目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/markets-fear-ecbs-cautious-path-risks-tipping-inflation-below-target-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果交易员的预测正确，那么欧洲央行现在就面临着因降息速度过慢而导致通胀率低于 2% 目标的风险，从而损害欧元区脆弱的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/markets-fear-ecbs-cautious-path-risks-tipping-inflation-below-target-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:04:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
